      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## moge_image_to_mesh\n\n**Single perspective photo → textured GLB**\n\n`Load Image` → subgraph `source_image` → `Save GLB`\n\n### Subgraph inputs\n| Port | Meaning |\n|------|--------|\n| `source_image` | RGB photo (auto-downscales if width > 2048) |\n| `inference_resolution` | MoGe detail 0–9 (9 = best) |\n| `inference_batch_size` | Images per GPU forward for multi-frame input; use **1** for one photo |\n| `mesh_frame_index` | Which inferred frame to mesh (0 for one image) |\n| `mesh_decimation` | Vertex stride (1 = full res) |\n| `mesh_gap_threshold` | Drop faces across depth jumps (0 = off) |\n| `mesh_texture` | Bake source colors into GLB |\n| `moge_model` | Checkpoint — see **Model Link** note |\n\n### Preview outputs\nEach `Preview Image` node is labeled with its map type in parentheses."
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
